WEBVTT

00:00:13.472 --> 00:00:17.726
<i>(PAT) The world will break your heart
ten ways to Sunday, that's guaranteed.</i>

00:00:17.893 --> 00:00:19.895
<i>And I can't begin to explain that.</i>

00:00:20.187 --> 00:00:23.774
<i>Or the craziness inside myself
and everybody else, but guess what.</i>

00:00:24.442 --> 00:00:27.445
<i>Sunday is my favourite day again.</i>

00:00:27.611 --> 00:00:32.992
<i>I think of everything everyone did
for me and I feel like a very lucky guy.</i>

